Text: Thank you so much for this!

TJSmith90210, I think this discography is only half complete.  Meaning, off the top of my head, I think The Echoing Green has about 14 albums floating around out there.  Unfortunately I only have the 7.  Hope there's still something within that you can enjoy just the same.  :)

Thanks again. Not to be greedy, but do you have any of the following: Dance House Children, mewithoutYou, Morella's Forest, Dakota Motor Co., or Danielson/Danielson Famile/Danielson Family/Brother Danielson (all the Danielson's are pretty much the same band, just different names).
